{{Quote|Smuggling phosovane salts. They use 'em as a base for pain killers on the Rim Worlds. These are medical supplies, Leia, they're&hellip;''"<br />"''&hellip;valuable, Mr. Solo.|[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]]|<ref name="The Pandora Effect">{{StoryCite|story=The Pandora Effect|book=The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 151}}</ref>}}
'''Phosovane salts''' were a base ingredient for pain-killer medicines commonly used on [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Rim Worlds]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] smuggled some from [[Daalang/Legends|Daalang]], under the nose of the local [[Torgaigne]] crime syndicate.

